# Festag Pop-ups & Modals

All centered dialogs use `components/Modal.tsx` + classes from `components/ui/festag-popup-styles.css`.

## Do

- **Surface:** `festag-popup-surface festag-modal-surface festag-modal-surface--{size}`
- **Backdrop:** `festag-modal-host` — shared dismiss hint on first overlay hover
- **Dark panel:** `--festag-black-popup` (#121214) via `--fp-bg` — not `var(--surface)`
- **Sizes:** `sm` 380 · `md` 480 · `lg` 640 · `xl` 820 · `form` 920×560 · `full` viewport
- **Header:** large H1 (`26px` desktop / `28px` mobile) — **one** title line only
- **Body:** T1 full sentence under the title (`15.5px` / mobile `16px`) — no Zwischenüberschrift
- **Form modals:** `size="form"`
- **Actions:** `<ModalButton>` / `.modal-cta` — 42px pill, Aeonik Regular, `white-space: nowrap`
- **Copy tokens:** `--fp-text`, `--fp-muted`, `--fp-divider`, `--fp-pill`

## Don't

- Inline `background: var(--surface)` on modal panels
- Custom one-off dialog shells with tiny titles
- Muted second H1 / stacked subtitle under the title

## Reference

Auth security, panel-switch, and recovery sheets share the same H1 → T1 → CTA language.
